==Seriously.[[WTF]]==
Boytaurs are the end result of Photoshop.  They're like [[furry|centaurs]], but rather than having a [[Mr. Hands|horse bottom,]] they have an extra set of human legs.  They may or may not have two [[cock|penii]]; it all depends on the [[faggotry]] of the "artist" in question.
